I noticed that when you mention a user in a comment, they only receive an email notification if they are mentioned in the first comment of an instance. However, if I reply to a comment and mention a user, they are not notified. I highly recommend you fix this, as any user would obviously need to know if they are mentioned. This is a great feature but won't be nearly as usable if not every user is notified when they are mentioned.

